<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="he"> <head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="description" content="Phoenix ltd error page"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"><title>Error Page</title><style>:root{--dark-blue: #111c3f;--accent-light: #fff;--light-blue: #eaf1ff}*{box-sizing:border-box}html{font-family:system-ui,sans-serif;background:var(--light-blue);padding:0;margin:0;height:100%;font-family:Ploni;direction:rtl}body{display:grid;grid-template-rows:100px 1fr 44px;height:100%;padding:0;margin:0}header,footer{background-color:var(--dark-blue);color:var(--accent-light);display:flex}header{justify-content:center;align-items:center}footer{justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding-inline:40px}footer ul{list-style:none;display:flex;gap:30px;margin:0}footer ul li a{color:var(--accent-light);text-decoration:none}header a{text-decoration:none;padding:0;margin:0}@media screen and (max-width: 991px){footer{justify-content:center}footer nav{display:none}}main{color:var(--dark-blue);display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;width:100%}h1{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;line-height:42px;margin:0 0 8px;padding:0}.error-code{font-size:16px;text-align:center;width:100%;font-weight:400;color:#6b6e77;max-width:600px}.content{display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:center;gap:24px;font-size:20px;line-height:23px;font-weight:400}.content img{margin-bottom:24px}.content-text{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;align-items:center;text-align:center}.content-text h1{margin:0}.content-text p{margin:0;padding:0}.service-mobile{display:none;padding:10px 25px 10px 30px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #111C3F;color:#111c3f;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;width:200px;border-radius:200px;margin-top:30px;margin-inline:auto;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:8px}.service-mobile img{margin:0}@media screen and (max-width: 991px){.content-text{gap:4px}.content-text h1{font-size:32px}.content-text p{font-size:18px}.service-mobile{display:flex}.service-desktop{display:none}}@font-face{font-family:Ploni;src:url(https://error.fnx.co.il/fonts/ploni-regular-aaa.woff2) format("woff2"),url(https://error.fnx.co.il/fonts/ploni-regular-aaa.woff) format("woff");font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-display:swap}@font-face{font-family:Ploni;src:url(https://error.fnx.co.il/fonts/ploni-medium-aaa.woff2) format("woff2"),url(https://error.fnx.co.il/fonts/ploni-medium-aaa.woff) format("woff");font-weight:500;font-style:normal;font-display:swap}@font-face{font-family:Ploni;src:url(https://error.fnx.co.il/fonts/ploni-bold-aaa.woff2) format("woff2"),url(https://error.fnx.co.il/fonts/ploni-bold-aaa.woff) format("woff");font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-display:swap}
</style></head> <body> <header> <a href="/"> <img src="https://error.fnx.co.il/images/phoenix_logo.png" alt="Phoenix logo"> </a> </header>  <main> <div class="content"> <img src="https://error.fnx.co.il/images/errorbg.png" alt="page background image"> <div class="content-text"> <h1>משהו השתבש</h1> <p> <span>
אנא נסו שנית במועד מאוחר יותר או פנו למוקד שירות הלקוחות
</span> <span dir="ltr" class="service-desktop">
*3455
</span> <a dir="rtl" class="service-mobile"> <img src="https://error.fnx.co.il/images/phone.png" alt="phone button icon"> <span>
שיחה עם נציג
</span> </a> </p> <p class="error-code" id="error-message"></p> </div> </div> </main>  <footer> <nav> <ul> <li> <a href="/security"> אבטחת מידע </a> </li> <li> <a href="/privacy"> מדיניות פרטיות </a> </li> <li> <a href="/terms"> תנאי שימוש </a> </li> </ul> </nav> <span> כל הזכויות שמורות להפניקס 2023 </span> </footer> </body></html>  